title: (3) Sections Of Assorted Pallet Racking with Contents Included: Assorted Metal

(3) Sections Of Assorted Pallet Racking with Contents Included: Assorted Metal

  • Includes:
  • (2) Sections of 6’ pallet racking with (4) 6’ uprights, (8) 6’ Crossmembers, and (4) 4’ Crossmembers

Removal Note: Buyer is responsible for all aspects of removal of this lot. No assistance of any kind will be provided by West Auctions. 

Removal Note: This lot is only available for removal July 14-18, 2025, from 9:00AM to 3:30PM each day. Removal appointments are required for pickup.
